description: "LEGO Biblea: Story of Daniel" (2014, Rated PG by no offical rating board) is a stop-motion animated short based off the histroical story found wothin the Holy Book of the Bible. It tells the tale of how a young Jewish boy gets taken from his home and how he puts his trust in God to find favor with Kings, and survive a night within a Den of Lions. Shot in 2009.
